{"tid":2291111,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港榮升全世界生活成本最貴城市","createTime":"2020-11-18T13:41:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T13:41:50.000Z","uid":363335,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f637c68f6d479f6ea32202be74faab8600c46199","tid":2291111,"uid":363335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T13:41:50.000Z","msg":"《經濟學人》旗下嘅「世界生活指數」發佈今年排名，香港一枝獨秀，擺脫新加坡同大阪，成爲世界生活成本最貴城市。<br />\n<br />\n研究學者表示，武漢肺炎疫情令移民勞工由新加坡出走，間接撳低咗樓價。另外，西歐生活成本今年普遍上升，美洲、非洲、東歐生活成本就有下跌趨勢。<br />\n<br />\nBBC 報導： <a href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-54983397\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-54983397&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5kPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=d232aa93\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-54983397</a><br />\n<br />\n大家準備好移民未？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n繼續留喺香港嘅準備好做一世樓奴之餘做埋共產黨奴隸未？  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}